{
    "background": "academy_co",
    "music": "academy",
    "default": "matsuda1",
    "frames": {
      "matsuda1": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "next": "this.matsuda2",
        "text": "Hey, there you are! I made it into the academy, too!"
      },
      "matsuda2": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "I thought you didn't want to come here?",
            "next": "this.matsuda3"
          },
          {
            "text": "Why would they let you in?",
            "next": "this.matsuda4"
          }
        ]
      },
      "matsuda3": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "next": "this.matsuda5",
        "text": "I mean, it’s pretty scary, and I'm still worried about the food and co-ed dorms and stuff. It's not going to be easy here, but nothing is easy, right?"
      },
      "matsuda4": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "next": "this.matsuda5",
        "text": "I mean, I probably shouldn't be here. But they looked at my transcripts and apparently I'm supposed to be really smart or something. I guess I just faked my way in by accident."
      },
      "matsuda5": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Chin up, it'll be great!",
            "next": "this.matsuda6"
          },
          {
            "text": "You <strong>really</strong> shouldn't be here.",
            "next": "this.matsuda7",
            "microscript": [
              {
                "variable": "matsuda",
                "add": -1
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "matsuda6": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "next": "this.matsuda8",
        "text": "Yeah, I guess. It'll be just like high school, right?"
      },
      "matsuda7": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "next": "this.matsuda8",
        "text": "Yeah, I guess. My mom will kill me if I don't at least give it a shot, though, so I'm stuck between a rock and a hard place."
      },
      "matsuda8": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "next": "this.matsuda9",
        "text": "Anyway, I have to go, uh, clear some stuff up with the registrar. Go introduce yourself to those girls, I know you’re thinking about it."
      },
      "matsuda9": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "matsuda",
        "nameText": "Matsuda Toyoda",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Way ahead of you, partner.",
            "next": "this.girls"
          },
          {
            "text": "[sarcastically] Wow, I never thought of it, good idea!",
            "next": "this.girls"
          }
        ]
      },
      "jen1": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "jen",
        "nameText": "Jen",
        "next": "this.jen2",
        "text": "Hi, I'm Jen! I'm from Almidia! You know, the kingdom that almost got invaded by the Dark Horde, and then we summoned those warriors and then they annexed us. Anyway... I like alchemy, soda fountains, fancy swords, action-dramedys, the Manic Pixie Dream Girls, and the Hexer series. I'm basically that hyper girl that's in everything, you know?"
      },
      "jen2": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "jen",
        "nameText": "Jen",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Yeah, you're talking too much.",
            "next": "this.jen3"
          },
          {
            "text": "No, it's fine.",
            "next": "this.jen4",
            "microscript": [
              {
                "affinity": "jen",
                "add": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "jen3": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "jen",
        "nameText": "Jen",
        "next": "this.jen5",
        "text": "Oh, really? Some people tell me that, but I never really thought I talked too much. I mean I'm saying a lot of words but it's not <em>that</em> many words, is it? Is this why I'm having so much trouble in the dating pool? I don't know, I just never thought it was a problem but I guess maybe it is?"
      },
      "jen4": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "jen",
        "nameText": "Jen",
        "next": "this.jen5",
        "text": "That's good. You see, some people tell me I talk too much, but I don't really think so. I mean I'm saying a lot of words but it's not <em>that</em> many words, is it? I am having a lot of trouble dating so maybe that's the problem, or maybe it's just a clash of personality thing?"
      },
      "jen5": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "jen",
        "nameText": "Jen",
        "next": "this.girls",
        "text": "Anyway... I should probably go say hi to my friends. That's what they told me I should say to leave a conversation, but I don't actually have any friends here. I mean there aren't many Almidians here, and this school is, like, <em>super</em> hard, so I'm like the one percent of one percent. I guess it's kind of cool but it's also a bit difficult. Well, it is for me, anyway-",
        "nextText": "I should go..."
      },
      "jane1": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": " ",
        "next": "this.jane2",
        "text": "It's a hell of a place, isn't it?"
      },
      "jane2": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": " ",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Yeah, it's definitely something!",
            "next": "this.jane3"
          },
          {
            "text": "I don't know, I just got here.",
            "next": "this.jane3",
            "microscript": [
              {
                "affinity": "joanna",
                "add": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "Eh, I've seen better.",
            "next": "this.jane3"
          }
        ]
      },
      "jane3": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton ",
        "next": "this.jane4",
        "text": "Joanna Slayton, Commander, Allied Earth Navy. Commander of the ASV Dieppe, or at least I was. No idea what the hell I'm doing here."
      },
      "jane4": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "I thought all of the students had to apply?",
            "next": "this.jane5"
          },
          {
            "text": "If you're standing here, you belong here, right?",
            "next": "this.jane6"
          }
        ]
      },
      "jane5": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton",
        "next": "this.jane7",
        "text": "Yeah, that's what I thought, too. Guess the galaxy just had to throw one more joke my way."
      },
      "jane6": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton",
        "next": "this.jane7",
        "text": "I didn't cheat my way in, if that's what you're asking. Passed all the entrance exams form art history to zero-g combat with flying colours. I just don't remember ever <em>applying</em> in the first place."
      },
      "jane7": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "You look a little young to be a Commander",
            "next": "this.jane8"
          },
          {
            "text": "Weren't you in that show with the teenaged spies?",
            "next": "this.jane9"
          }
        ]
      },
      "jane8": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton",
        "nextText": "Slayton.",
        "next": "this.jane11",
        "text": "Let's see, last birthday I celebrated was my 30th. But I was born in 2154, which is a century and a half in the <em>future</em>. Something went wrong in all the timey-wimey stuff, I guess."
      },
      "jane9": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton",
        "nextText": "Slayton.",
        "next": "this.jane11",
        "text": "Uh, no, I don't think so. I've just got one of those voices you hear all the time."
      },
      "jane11": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "joanna",
        "nameText": "Joanna Slayton",
        "next": "this.girls",
        "text": "Matsutake."
      },
      "weiss1": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": " ",
        "next": "this.weiss2",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      "weiss2": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": " ",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Sorry, just trying to make conversation",
            "next": "this.weiss3"
          },
          {
            "text": "Are you always a cold bitch?",
            "next": "this.weiss4"
          },
          {
            "microscript": [
              {
                "affinity": "floretta",
                "add": -1
              }
            ],
            "text": "Nothing",
            "next": "this.girls"
          }
        ]
      },
      "weiss3": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": " ",
        "next": "this.weiss5",
        "text": "I know. Sorry, I've just got a lot on my mind. Even with my sister in charge, there's still a lot going on back home with the Company. I've heard mixed things about this place, and I'm still waiting on a very important piece of luggage."
      },
      "weiss4": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": " ",
        "next": "this.girls",
        "text": "And are you always this much of a jackass?"
      },
      "weiss5": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": " ",
        "text": "So, your name is...",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "Janet",
            "next": "this.weiss6"
          },
          {
            "text": "Jessica",
            "next": "this.weiss6"
          },
          {
            "text": "Juliet",
            "next": "this.weiss6"
          },
          {
            "text": "Joyst",
            "next": "this.weiss6"
          }
        ]
      },
      "weiss6": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": "Floretta Speer",
        "next": "this.weiss7",
        "text": "It's Floretta. Floretta <em>Speer</em>. As in the Speer Dustwerk, the largest supplier of energy in the world."
      },
      "weiss7": {
        "type": "choice",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": "Floretta Hess",
        "choices": [
          {
            "text": "I'll admit, I wasn't expecting that",
            "next": "this.weiss8"
          },
          {
            "text": "In the flesh?",
            "next": "this.weiss8"
          },
          {
            "text": "Hi, Floretta.",
            "next": "this.weiss8"
          }
        ]
      },
      "weiss8": {
        "type": "text",
        "image": "floretta",
        "nameText": "Floretta Hess",
        "next": "this.weiss9",
        "text": "Like this Academy, I'm full of surprises"
      },
      "weiss9": {
        "type": "text",
